---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Pottery and Candle Combo Session"
  description="Experience both pottery and candle making in one creative session in Centerville, TN. Double the creativity, double the fun!"
  price="$35-45 per person"
  duration="2.5-3 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="pottery candle combo, art combo classes, creative experiences, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h1>Pottery and Candle Combo Session - Centerville, TN</h1>
    <p>Why choose one when you can do both? Our Pottery and Candle Combo Session offers an extended creative experience combining pottery painting and candle making in one memorable session.</p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>You'll start by painting pre-made pottery pieces, then transition to creating hand-poured candles with custom colors and scents. It's the best of both creative worlds in one afternoon or evening!</p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Pre-made pottery piece painting</li>
      <li>Professional glazing and kiln-firing of pottery</li>
      <li>Hand-poured candle creation</li>
      <li>Fragrance and color selection</li>
      <li>All supplies and materials</li>
      <li>Expert instruction for both activities</li>
      <li>Take home finished candles immediately</li>
      <li>Pottery shipped or picked up later</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Families wanting extended creative time</li>
      <li>Art enthusiasts wanting variety</li>
      <li>Groups and celebrations</li>
      <li>Anyone wanting maximum creativity!</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Session Breakdown</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Welcome and intro (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>Pottery painting (50 minutes)</li>
      <li>Break and transition (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Candle making (60 minutes)</li>
      <li>Finishing up (15 minutes)</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $35-45 per person<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 2.5-3 hours<br />
      <strong>Group Size:</strong> 1-8 people<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> All levels welcome
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Experience both art forms!</strong> Call (931) 729-8459 or email made@thelocalplacetn.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Best creative combo ever! We got to try pottery AND candles in one visit. Left with amazing creations!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>The Anderson Family</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Our group loved doing both activities. So much fun and great value for the time!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Lisa's Art Group</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"The combo format kept everyone engaged the whole time. Never a dull moment!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Emily & Family</strong> - Franklin (35 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="related">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Paint and Pour Pottery Candle</h3>
        <p>Combine pottery painting with candle making for double the creativity.</p>
        <a href="/art-studio/paint-and-pour-pottery-candle" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Family Pottery Painting Experience</h3>
        <p>Multi-generational creative fun with pottery painting for the whole family.</p>
        <a href="/art-studio/family-pottery-painting-experience" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Kids Candle Making Class</h3>
        <p>Safe, fun candle-making experiences designed for children.</p>
        <a href="/art-studio/kids-candle-making-class" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
